OS X Mavericks 10.9.2 Build 13C53


Apple has seeded build 13C53 of OS X Mavericks 10.9.2 to developers.

The latest build arrives just a week after the company released OS X Mavericks 10.9.2 build 13C48.
As was the case in the earlier beta, Apple is again asking developers to focus on Mail.

Ever since OS X debuted last October, there has been a steady stream of complaints about the Mail app, especially when using it with Gmail accounts.
